text: Matteo Malucelli (born 20 October 1993) is an Italian cyclist, who currently rides for UCI ProTeam . For the 2021 season, Malucelli will join the team. ==Major results== ;2015 : 1st Stage 3 Rás Tailteann : 1st Stage 10 Volta a Portugal : 3rd Circuito del Porto : 6th Trofej Umag ;2016 : Tour du Maroc ::1st Points classification ::1st Stages 3, 4 & 6 : 1st Stage 1 Okolo Slovenska : 8th GP Kranj ;2017 : Tour of Bihor ::1st Points classification ::1st Stages 1 & 3 : 1st Stage 2 Okolo Slovenska ;2018 : Vuelta al Táchira ::1st Stages 1 & 3 : 1st Stage 2 Vuelta a Aragón : 1st Stage 2 Tour de Bretagne ;2019 : 1st 20px Points classification Tour Poitou-Charentes en Nouvelle-Aquitaine ==References== ==External links== * Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Italian male cyclists
